Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:04.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 我和静组合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 为了女主角党知名度的提升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,希望二位能配合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可以可以 这个可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那 谁逗谁捧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:21.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这…组合的意思是唱歌 不是相声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:26.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静 还请多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我并没有与人组队的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:32.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:35.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月的搭档的话 还是去找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别介意 别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个暂且不提 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里有营销的工作给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你肯定会接的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:56.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,营销?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:05.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你闪耀的光芒是绝对无法和他人融合的双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:08.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,无论发生什么 我都不会被打败的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:10.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一日局长?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:05.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么我一定要给照顾那些偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 听说这次的一日局长特别可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:16.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 反正都是个卖乖的任性小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:22.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是今天担当一日局长的星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好萌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我将追随你一生!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,变脸真快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:37.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好 一起去巡逻吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是 一日局长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,非法停自行车 逮捕你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:44.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,走路玩手机 逮捕你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:49.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,乱扔垃圾 逮捕你了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:53.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让她当一日局长真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸小姐应该更合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有什么关系啊 制服也很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真好 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也想成为那气球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您说什么傻话 小野寺警官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好的 拍到偶像议员的OO了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:35.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偷拍什么的 绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,竟敢偷拍我们局长 真是吃了豹子胆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,犯下多起猥琐案的重要通缉犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:50.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么? 真不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,期待你今后的表现 小野寺君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是立大功了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这也是多亏了一日局长 谢谢您!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:03.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,本部发来信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,龟龟幼儿园 发生了劫持人质事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:08.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,人质是慰问担当一日园长的偶像议员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,若叶党的天羽来叶议员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,以及 同伴若叶党的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:19.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,清水由奈 雨宫唯奈 三人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,若叶党的人被劫持?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:27.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,集合全局人员 停止手上的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:28.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:32.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是一日局长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:53.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们已经完全被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:09.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,立即释放人质 投降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么办 小野寺警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:20.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样下去人质就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:23.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一日局长?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:31.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不 这怎么说也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:34.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而且犯人的正面目也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:34.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,已经查明犯人身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:43.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,劫持三名人质的是 龟龟幼儿园的儿童
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,儿童?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:46.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,犯人…儿童联系了警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要求撤回龟龟幼儿园的关闭决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:57.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,否则 就对人质做过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请问 关闭幼儿园是怎么一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:14.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,本来龟龟幼儿园因为持续的财政亏损 经营难以维系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,政府又削减了预算 减少了扶持金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幼儿园已经决定开到这个月为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么办 小野寺警官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:31.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,劫持犯是儿童的话 也不能让突击队直接冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:34.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有什么好主意的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一日局长 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总之 我先去听听他们怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:46.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您等等 总部没下达许可 你不能随意行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:55.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,案件不是发生在会议室 而是幼儿园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那句话 是抄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,媒体来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听到风吹早动就赶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不妙 实在不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:16.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个 能和我谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是一日局长 星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:24.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我想和犯人们直接对话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.54,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那就打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:46.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这什么啊 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们要用这个干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一日局长 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:07.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,相信她吧 她的话肯定能找到突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,警官 刚刚收到联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,儿童们把一日局长也劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不会吧 我晕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小野寺警官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了 为什么不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,父亲大人 要谈的事是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:28.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:33.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也罢 那我就单刀直入了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静 是不是该回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,搞什么偶像 做我的继承人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,唱歌跳舞什么的 玩够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您想谈的事就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还能有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:53.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像不是能做一辈子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:57.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这么简单的道理 聪明的你应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要多看看现实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您想说的就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有其他的事的话 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:17.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你是… 若叶党的天羽来叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还有 清水由奈和雨宫唯奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们不是被劫持做人质了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我只能想出这招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为了这幼儿园不被关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:43.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女主角党的星菜夏月也被儿童们劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:46.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,儿童们的母亲也纷纷来到案发现场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,场面十分混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:52.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小真 别做傻事 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:56.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小惠 你现在做的事很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,把我的一日局长还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,求您冷静点好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:07.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,楼凯党的伽理亚议员也来到了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,伽理亚议员 您来这的目的是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对于这场骚动 请发表一下看法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,闹得还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:21.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是可悲 小小年纪就干出绑架这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真想看看家长是个什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你说什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:28.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,发生这种事 归根结底还不是你造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,关掉这里 改成购物中心?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 所以扶持金也被削减了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明显就是楼凯党的那些龌龊的大人们干出来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别生气 由奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:48.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这里的孩子 家里基本上是父母双工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以在妈妈下班之前 只能在这里等待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 楼凯党的那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:59.22,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这里的孩子们 就像一家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:04.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是 如果这个幼儿园没有了 这些孩子们该何去何从呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:08.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,家人是不能轻易改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以说 别动不动就哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:18.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,孩子们寄放在哪里? 根本没有寄放的必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:18.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从一开始女人这样的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,结婚之后就该在家庭里专心抚养孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:31.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说什么没有能寄放孩子的地方 所以没法工作养育不了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:33.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这才是本末倒置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你在说什么 脑子进水了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:41.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,完全没看清现实 我们不工作的话要怎么养育孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以才要建商业中心啊 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,关掉这里改建商业中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,税收增加了 也能多出工作岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:53.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从结果来看 各个家庭的收入也会提高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样一来 母亲就没有工作的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:03.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我有哪里讲错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:07.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好 驳倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:12.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,妈妈们应该一直想和孩子们在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:17.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让她们不工作什么的 不就和让她们不养孩子一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的 绝对不能原谅他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:23.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,孩子们知道这里有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能让什么都不懂的大人们单方面决定关掉幼儿园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:35.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是 没想到事情会闹得这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 把你也卷了进来 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来叶不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是 来叶没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是我们拜托你帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是啊 为了这些孩子也不能在这半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们进退与共
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:06.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 我无论如何都想保护这些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以 你能帮帮我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,龟龟幼儿园的孩子们仍然坚守不出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:19.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在成为人质的偶像议员星菜夏月出现在了凉台上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看起来是要转达犯人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:30.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个 现在开始转达犯人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果不在一个小时之内…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:38.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,承认留存幼儿园的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就要把我们的人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就把我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就把我们全都杀死…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,诶 不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能杀了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个 搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不杀 但是要做很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:06.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜托了各位 请救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:10.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小野寺警官 情况紧急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.17,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真是搞不懂最近的孩子们都在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说什么不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,局长肯定会想办法解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要是能接受要求就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,星菜真软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也不是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,总觉得我一个人的话就不太…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.44,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 你干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,突击? 太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:42.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对方可是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:47.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不 劫持人质坚守不出 这和恐怖分子没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要采取相同的对应手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:52.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,责任我来担 现在立刻突击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,突击…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:58.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:04.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀 难得的休假日 还特意来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,难道是担心夏月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:11.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来龙去脉我听星月讲了 现在是什么情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:16.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还是不出来啊 不知道要在里面待到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:20.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请问 您是一日局长的相关人士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,刚刚警察说要进行突击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,您是?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是里面的孩子的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:28.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,突击?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:29.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这话是为你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:35.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,告诉若叶党的三人 也不要再强撑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸小姐 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:42.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是天羽来叶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:46.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有这里 孩子们就没有栖身之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,而且妈妈们也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可是万一受伤了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:55.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以静也来帮忙吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一日局长 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:03.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,突击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,第一波从院子过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:08.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从院子里过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:16.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:24.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:30.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是… 用过的尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让你们尝尝什么叫走狗屎运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,气球?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,特制胡椒气球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是粘鸟胶 动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,陷阱战术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:57.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,警察虽然开始了突击 但是全部以失败告终
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,孩子们现在仍在幼儿园固守不出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,被一群孩子整成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:06.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,听好了 现在开始突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有蜜蜂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,蜜蜂? 管那些干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.90,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有什么能制造烟的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用我车上的发烟筒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:29.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,伤没有大碍 也没有过敏性休克的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,保险起见 检查下有没有磕到头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,眼睛跟着手指走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,抱歉 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哪里 那边没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:54.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那些人到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是孩子们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然担心仍守在里面的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,眼前有伤者还是会来照顾
